OL,3,CTeenagers arrested after baby left
OL,4,Cwith serious injuries
OL,6,FA teenage boy and girl have been
OL,7,Farrested after a baby was left with
OL,8,Fserious injuries.
OL,10,FPolice received a report that a baby
OL,11,Fhad been presented at hospital with
OL,12,Fserious injuries in the early hours of
OL,13,FMonday 9 March.
OL,15,FDetective Inspector Gemma Walker said:
OL,16,F"An investigation has been launched
OL,17,Fwhilst we carry out multiple lines of
OL,18,Fenquiry to establish the full
OL,19,Fcircumstances surrounding the baby's
OL,20,Finjuries, which are currently being
OL,21,Ftreated as unexplained.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
