OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1773176767
OL,3,CTeenagers arrested after baby left
OL,4,Cwith serious injuries
OL,6,F"A scene guard has been put in place
OL,7,Fat an address in Grimsby as our
OL,8,Finvestigations continue and to allow
OL,9,Fofficers to carry out their enquiries.
OL,11,F"A teenage boy and girl have both been
OL,12,Farrested in connection to the
OL,13,Fincident, and I would ask that people
OL,14,Fplease refrain from any form of
OL,15,Fspeculation as enquiries remain
OL,16,Fongoing"
OL,18,FIf you have any information that may
OL,19,Fassist our investigation, please
OL,20,Fcontact police on 101 quoting log 26
OL,21,Fof 9 March.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
